<li>4/1/95 <a href="/heritage/library/categories/family/pr1toler.html">Fisher of Men: A Baltimore Minister Promotes Black Christian Manhood</a> by <a href="/heritage/staff/toler.htm">Herbert H. Toler Jr.</a> (Spring 1995 Policy Review) 

<li>7/29/92 <a href= "/heritage/library/categories/crimelaw/lect401.html">Crime, Poverty and the Family</a> by The Honorable William P. Barr. (Heritage Lecture No. 401)
<li>7/23/91 <a href="/heritage/library/categories/family/lect345.html">Children and Family in America: Challenges For The 1990s</a> by Wade F. Horn, Ph.D. (Heritage Lecture No. 345)
</ul>
<p>
<br>
